welcome_message_body: Welcome to Lienen, Germany! Get ready to discover the charming beauty of our small town, known for its picturesque landscapes and rich history. We invite you to explore and immerse yourself in all that Lienen has to offer. Enjoy your stay!

wifi.note: Passengers can enjoy free WiFi throughout the airport with a simple registration process.
